And all of these employees seem to be trained to do everything, so if you

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:43.110
ask to see the manager, you might find him or her mopping up some spilled

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:48.000
milk or stacking the shelves or even scanning products at the checkout till.

